  "lyrics": "Oh, yeah, oh, yeah, oh, yeah, yeah, hey You got a lot of nerve, don't you, baby? I only fit the curve Cause you made me your tail And all your friends said I'm crazy Like I'm the only one Why'd you throw them stones at you? Had a wild hair of your own or two Ridding your big glass hand with a view I thought you knew I had some hope It ain't like I can make this kind of mess all by myself Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell They said teamwork makes it framework And I asked for help Help, yeah You thought I'd take the blame for us to crumble And go around like you ain't guilty Of something already lost The game that you've been running Guess it's catching up to you You think that you're so innocent After all the shit that you did I ain't an angel, you ain't heaven sent Can't wash my hands of this, I had some help It ain't like I can make this kind of mess all by myself Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell They said teamwork makes it framework Can't wash my hands Oh yeah, I had You know I had some help It takes two to break a heart in two You blame me and baby I blame you Hey, it's the truth, I had some help Made this kind of mess all by myself Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell They said teamwork makes it framework And I asked for help I asked for help with you, baby I asked for help with you And now I ain't Never going back again, bro",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 15,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, oh, yeah, oh, yeah, yeah, hey",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 19.940000534057617,
      "text": "You got a lot of nerve, don't you, baby?",
      "start": 15.699999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 22.739999771118164,
      "text": "I only fit the curve",
      "start": 20.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 24.65999984741211,
      "text": "Cause you made me your tail",
      "start": 22.739999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 27.399999618530273,
      "text": "And all your friends said I'm crazy",
      "start": 24.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 30.6200008392334,
      "text": "Like I'm the only one",
      "start": 27.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 34.400001525878906,
      "text": "Why'd you throw them stones at you?",
      "start": 31.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 38.52000045776367,
      "text": "Had a wild hair of your own or two",
      "start": 35.439998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 42.13999938964844,
      "text": "Ridding your big glass hand with a view",
      "start": 38.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 44.81999969482422,
      "text": "I thought you knew",
      "start": 42.5
    },
    {
      "end": 46.20000076293945,
      "text": "I had some hope",
      "start": 44.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 49.900001525878906,
      "text": "It ain't like I can make this kind of mess all by myself",
      "start": 46.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 53.68000030517578,
      "text": "Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf",
      "start": 49.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 57.41999816894531,
      "text": "Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell",
      "start": 53.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 59.599998474121094,
      "text": "They said teamwork makes it framework",
      "start": 57.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 62.13999938964844,
      "text": "And I asked for help",
      "start": 59.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 66,
      "text": "Help, yeah",
      "start": 64.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 72.31999969482422,
      "text": "You thought I'd take the blame for us to crumble",
      "start": 68.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 75.4000015258789,
      "text": "And go around like you ain't guilty",
      "start": 72.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 78.12000274658203,
      "text": "Of something already lost",
      "start": 75.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 79.95999908447266,
      "text": "The game that you've been running",
      "start": 78.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 82.62000274658203,
      "text": "Guess it's catching up to you",
      "start": 80.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 87.13999938964844,
      "text": "You think that you're so innocent",
      "start": 83.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 91.44000244140625,
      "text": "After all the shit that you did",
      "start": 87.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 95.0199966430664,
      "text": "I ain't an angel, you ain't heaven sent",
      "start": 91.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 98.72000122070312,
      "text": "Can't wash my hands of this, I had some help",
      "start": 95.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 102.41999816894531,
      "text": "It ain't like I can make this kind of mess all by myself",
      "start": 98.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 106.22000122070312,
      "text": "Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf",
      "start": 102.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 109.94000244140625,
      "text": "Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell",
      "start": 106.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 112.13999938964844,
      "text": "They said teamwork makes it framework",
      "start": 109.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 114.13999938964844,
      "text": "Can't wash my hands",
      "start": 112.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 119.12000274658203,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I had",
      "start": 117.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 123.54000091552734,
      "text": "You know",
      "start": 122.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 126.12000274658203,
      "text": "I had some help",
      "start": 124.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 133.1999969482422,
      "text": "It takes two to break a heart in two",
      "start": 127.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 140.13999938964844,
      "text": "You blame me and baby I blame you",
      "start": 135.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 143.66000366210938,
      "text": "Hey, it's the truth, I had some help",
      "start": 141.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 147.3800048828125,
      "text": "Made this kind of mess all by myself",
      "start": 144.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 151.1999969482422,
      "text": "Don't act like you ain't helped me put that bottle on the shelf",
      "start": 147.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 154.89999389648438,
      "text": "Been deep in every week and if you couldn't tell",
      "start": 151.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 157.16000366210938,
      "text": "They said teamwork makes it framework",
      "start": 154.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 158.66000366210938,
      "text": "And I asked for help",
      "start": 157.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 163.8800048828125,
      "text": "I asked for help with you, baby",
      "start": 161.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 168.3800048828125,
      "text": "I asked for help with you",
      "start": 164.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 170.8000030517578,
      "text": "And now I ain't",
      "start": 168.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 173.72000122070312,
      "text": "Never going back again, bro",
      "start": 170.8000030517578
